Task 4.2: Create ActionBar (Cancel + Save Changes)

Summary: Extracted inline action bar from ConfigurationView into a standalone
ActionBar view with onCancel/onSave closure callbacks. Added saveChanges() and
discardChanges() methods to ConfigurationViewModel. Cancel reverts settings to
persisted UserDefaults values and reloads habits. Save persists current settings.

Created files:
- ductiva/ActionBar.swift — Standalone action bar view
- ductivaTests/ActionBarTests.swift — 5 tests (smoke, callbacks, labels)

Modified files:
- ductiva/ConfigurationView.swift — Replaced inline action bar with ActionBar
- ductiva/ConfigurationViewModel.swift — Added saveChanges(), discardChanges()
- ductivaTests/ConfigurationViewModelTests.swift — Added 3 tests for save/discard

Why: Completes Phase 4 requirement to wire Cancel/Save functionality and
extract into a reusable, testable component.
